               <p>JOSHUA FLIGHT. I am <rs id="t18300415-301-viclabel1641" type="occupation">bar-man at a wine-vaults</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-301-victim2530 t18300415-301-viclabel1641"></join>. The prisoner was <rs id="t18300415-301-deflabel1642" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-301-defend2528 t18300415-301-deflabel1642"></join> to me for twelve months; she left me without notice, and I missed this property.</p>
